OL,3,CWaiting list for routine NHS
OL,4,Ctreatments at lowest since 2022
OL,6,FThe waiting list for routine hospital
OL,7,Ftreatments in England is at its lowest
OL,8,Fsince summer 2022, as the NHS makes
OL,9,F"real inroads" in ending long medical
OL,10,Fdelays.
OL,12,FAround 7.11 million treatments were
OL,13,Fwaiting to be carried out at the end
OL,14,Fof March, relating to 6.02 million
OL,15,Fpatients - down from 7.22 million
OL,16,Ftreatments and 6.11 million patients
OL,17,Fat the end of February, NHS data shows.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
