PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778796671
OL,3,CWaiting list for routine NHS
OL,4,Ctreatments at lowest since 2022
OL,6,FIt was the lowest number of treatments
OL,7,Fwaiting since August 2022, when it
OL,8,Fstood at 7.07 million, according to
OL,9,Fthe figures - and February to March
OL,10,Fwas also the largest month-on-month
OL,11,Fdrop for treatments since April 2020.
OL,13,FAn estimated 65.3% of patients in
OL,14,FEngland also began hospital treatment
OL,15,Fwithin 18 weeks of referral in March,
OL,16,Fthe highest percentage achieved by the
OL,17,Fhealth service since November 2021,
OL,18,FNHS data shows.
OL,20,FIt is the NHS target to treat patients
OL,21,Fin 18 weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
