OL,3,CWaiting list for routine NHS
OL,4,Ctreatments at lowest since 2022
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FA total of 79.4% patients who received
OL,12,Fan urgent referral for suspected
OL,13,Fcancer were either diagnosed or had
OL,14,Fthe disease ruled out within 28 days
OL,15,Fin March, slightly down from 80.5% in
OL,16,FFebruary, but above the NHS target of
OL,17,F75%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
