OL,3,CWaiting list for routine NHS
OL,4,Ctreatments at lowest since 2022
OL,6,FThere were 72.8% of patients who began
OL,7,Ftheir first definitive treatment for
OL,8,Fcancer in March within 62 days of an
OL,9,Furgent referral - up from 68.6% in
OL,10,FFebruary.
OL,12,FThe number of patients facing the
OL,13,Flongest waits for treatment was also
OL,14,Fat its lowest for six years, NHS
OL,15,FEngland said.
OL,17,FAt the end of March, there were 94,406
OL,18,Fpeople who had been waiting more than
OL,19,Fa year to start routine hospital, down
OL,20,Ffrom 122,668 at the end of February.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
