OL,3,CWaiting list for routine NHS
OL,4,Ctreatments at lowest since 2022
OL,6,FNHS CEO Sir Jim Mackey said the data
OL,7,Fshowed the health service is "making
OL,8,Freal inroads on the things that
OL,9,Fmatter" to patients.
OL,11,F"This is a huge moment for the NHS,"
OL,12,Fsaid Mackey, who also noted that last
OL,13,Fyear was the busiest NHS winter on
OL,14,Frecord.
OL,16,F"Hitting our targets for the first
OL,17,Ftime in years hasn't happened by
OL,18,Faccident ` it's been down to an
OL,19,Fabsolutely enormous effort from NHS
OL,20,Fstaff up and down the country."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
