OL,3,CWaiting list for routine NHS
OL,4,Ctreatments at lowest since 2022
OL,6,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said
OL,7,Fthere was still "lots more to do" as
OL,8,Fhe praised the figures.
OL,10,F"Our plan for the NHS is working. This
OL,11,Fis the biggest cut in waiting lists in
OL,12,Fa single month in 17 years," Streeting
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"It means we are right on track to
OL,16,Fdeliver the fastest reduction in
OL,17,Fwaiting times in the history of the
OL,18,FNHS.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778796671
OL,3,CWaiting list for routine NHS
OL,4,Ctreatments at lowest since 2022
OL,6,F"That is thanks to the government's
OL,7,Finvestment, modernisation, and the
OL,8,Fremarkable efforts of staff right
OL,9,Facross the country. Lots done, lots
OL,10,Fmore to do."
OL,12,FStreeting is reportedly considering
OL,13,Fresigning from his role as health
OL,14,Fsecretary in order to make a bid to
OL,15,Freplace Prime Minister Keir Starmer.
OL,17,FStarmer has been facing pressure to
OL,18,Fleave Downing Street after Labour
OL,19,Fsuffered catastrophic losses in the
OL,20,Flocal and devolved elections last week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
