OL,3,CWaiting list for routine NHS
OL,4,Ctreatments at lowest since 2022
OL,6,FStreeting and the PM sat down for
OL,7,Fcrunch talks in No 10 earlier on
OL,8,FWednesday, which lasted just 16
OL,9,Fminutes.
OL,11,FIf Streeting mounts a challenge, he
OL,12,Fwill need the support of 81 Labour MPs
OL,13,Fto begin a formal contest.
OL,15,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,16,Four political experts are across all
OL,17,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,18,Fto the latest episode below...
